(24, 'Details on legislation ', 'binary', 1, 0, 'Legislation, Principles and Institutional setting', 'Planning', 'Resources', 'System', 0, 'To be replaced by the SDG indicator has national statistical legislation that complies with the Fundamental Principles of Official Statistics', 'PARIS21 ', 'Statistical legislation details, link to statistical law, compliance with the UN principles, etc. ', '', 0, ''),
