(118, 'Statistical Law / Act', 'binary', 1, 0, 'Legislation, Principles and Institutional setting', 'Planning', 'Resources', 'System', 0, '', 'PARIS21', 'The Statistics Act gives the NSO the authority to collect, compile, analyze, abstract, and publish information on the economic, social and general conditions of the country and its citizens on bhalf of the National government', '', 0, ''),
