(131, 'Vital registration', 'binary', 1, 0, 'Statistical production processes', 'Production', 'Skills & Knowledge', 'Organization', 1, '', 'World Bank Statistical Capacity Indicator', 'Quality of vital registration data and system coverage. Vital registration systems record the occurrence and characteristics of vital events pertaining to the population and serve as a main source of vital statistics. Countries with complete vital statistics registries may have more accurate and timely demographic indicators.', 'indicator (0 or 1)', 1, ''),
